nodes.text: Zulay Ulor was a human female who led Caracara Squadron, a mercenary starfighter squadron. Ulor's squadron offered defense services to systems without their own fleets, but had been chased out of restricted zones by both the First Order and New Republic prior to the outbreak of war.
Zulay Ulor wore a dark suit with a flight helmet in Caracara Squadron colors. She flew a refurbished U-wing starfighter.
